# ============================================================
# .gitignore 분류 기준: "누가/무엇이 생성하는가"
# ============================================================
# 1. Environment   — 개발 환경이 생성 (OS, IDE, Editor, Logs)
# 2. macOS App     — Swift / Xcode 빌드 산출물 및 사용자 상태
# 3. Agents        — Python 에이전트 툴체인이 생성
# 4. DB            — 데이터베이스 / 데이터 파일
# 5. AI / Agent    — AI 도구가 생성 (Claude, Codex, Gemini 등)
# 6. Infra         — 환경 변수, 시크릿, 배포 관련
# 7. Documentation — 팀 내부 문서, 초안, 노트
# ============================================================


# ========================= 1. Environment ===========================

## OS - macOS
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon

## OS - Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

## IDE / Editor
.vscode/
.cursor/
.antiglarity/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.project
.classpath
.c9/

## Logs
*.log
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt


# ========================= 2. macOS App (Swift / Xcode) =========================

## Build Artifacts
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM
*.dSYM.zip

## Swift macro / 자동 생성 소스
swift-generated-sources/

## Xcode - User-specific (개인 UI 상태, 브레이크포인트 등)
xcuserdata/
*.xcodeproj/xcuserdata/
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcuserstatev2
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Swift Package Manager
.swiftpm/
.build/
Packages/

## CocoaPods / Carthage (사용 시 대비)
Pods/
Carthage/Build/
Carthage/Checkouts/

## fastlane (사용 시 대비)
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output


# ========================= 3. Agents (Python) =========================

## Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

## Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

## Packaging / Cache
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/


# ============================== 4. DB ===============================

## Database Files (development)
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db

## Data Files (CSV, Excel exports)
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xls


# ====================== 5. AI / Agent Tools =========================

## Claude
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/docs-file.json
.claude/**/*.bak.*

## Codex
# .codex/

## Gemini
# .gemini/

## Opencode
# .agent/
# .opencode/

## Sisyphus
# .sisyphus/

## Graphify
# graphify-out/


# ============================= 6. Infra =============================

## Environment Variables
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

## Secrets / Keys
*.pem
*.key

## Security Scan Reports
trivy-reports/


# ========================= 7. Documentation ==========================

## Project Documentation (internal/draft)
docs/
